item.title: MeetBSD 2018
item.description: MeetBSD 2018 (https://www.meetbsd.com/), Intel Campus, Santa Clara, CA, United States 2018 年 10 月 19 - 20 日. MeetBSD 2018 is a mixed unConference format event featuring both scheduled talks and community-driven events such as birds-of-a-feather meetings and speed geeking sessions.
